<p>Once you have a degree or equivalent qualification you’re ready for postgraduate primary or secondary initial teacher training courses. You will get the teaching qualifications you need by completing your course.</p>

<p>You also need the following GCSEs at grade 4 (C) or above, or equivalent qualifications:</p>

<ul>
  <li>English</li>
  <li>maths</li>
  <li>science if you want to teach primary</li>
</ul>

<p>You may be able to show you meet the standard in another way if you do not have GCSEs.</p>

<p>For advice on the qualifications you need for teaching, chat to our teacher training experts online. They're available Monday to Friday between 8:30am and 5:30pm.</p>

